[{"Code":"en","Title":"Your dashboard","Slug":"your-dashboard","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"1baf028f-db08-459c-8a96-8e572e47a76a\">Once you've created an account, you'll be directed to your dashboard. Before you start creating transactions, it's important to understand that your dashboard has two modes:</p><ul data-block-id=\"db62505f-8847-4ea8-b55d-73a55ba93a01\"><li data-block-id=\"6db24df9-35b4-4fb2-983e-62ec68a36d78\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"a69fd403-4dd4-4a5d-9194-4da35d60315b\"><strong>Test Mode</strong>: Experiment and familiarize yourself with our features or test your integration thoroughly using virtual funds. In test mode, your transactions does not transact with real money, so you can safely test different features and functionalities of before launching into live production.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7b9091c2-a4d1-40f9-aa33-e94305dbad90\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"6b68c8b3-00f0-4ade-b44c-71a902d5dfb6\"><strong>Live Mode</strong>: Accept and process real payments from your customers. This mode becomes available after your account has been activated.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"c91cfcb6-83b1-4743-adee-5fc9deb347bd\">You’ll see a label on the bottom left corner of your dashboard under your business logo that clearly indicates whether you're currently in Test Mode or Live Mode.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"731d01d2-ea77-4747-aeeb-51869049cd8c\"><strong>How to switch dashboard modes</strong></h2><ol data-block-id=\"60b47698-460f-42f1-b8e8-5cf1e4b1aa46\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f93aaf72-e8ea-49a0-9fc8-da4a8c9543ce\"><p data-block-id=\"05b55174-79a7-43fe-959e-d7b536e9d4b9\">Click your&nbsp;<strong>business name</strong>&nbsp;in the bottom left corner of the dashboard</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d51bd7e1-01ee-46d4-b770-dbdcd6b01f4c\"><p data-block-id=\"37b684b3-eff4-48f7-8564-6c3c98d09afe\">Toggle the&nbsp;<strong>Switch to Test / Live Mode&nbsp;</strong>option on or off as needed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"55fc5990-d0e0-4d13-862e-4286d059fc20\"><p data-block-id=\"b178d42c-f2af-43c7-a153-cc92b6c3ae34\">When you switch to Test Mode, it will only <strong>apply for your own dashboard and not your team members’</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"c3ee80af-ada5-4005-86ae-f9b148193956\"><p data-block-id=\"41e342db-5883-4a08-96cc-97cfbd1677aa\">In Live Mode, you can choose to switch back to Test Mode as well—this will not erase your activity on Live Mode</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"f516f836-6be5-4df1-91cc-17c001599550\">Your business and profile details</h2><p data-block-id=\"292d91b9-30bb-40e3-9cd4-a3d1677c9f04\">To view your business and profile details, click <strong>Edit Profile</strong>. The information that you submitted when you create your account and verify your details will be shown under <strong>Your Business</strong>. If you’d like to update any of these details, please contact <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a></p><p data-block-id=\"9538c31c-4c86-4f25-aa47-d534b7b4c7db\">Under <strong>Your Profile</strong>, you will be able to see the following details:</p><ul data-block-id=\"8010ac86-272d-4906-b0a1-082b5dafc72c\"><li data-block-id=\"2a8971c4-1f68-41bb-b628-11d8cd604750\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"667aecca-2868-4ae8-9a7b-6ac8e25f675b\"><strong>Email: </strong>Email you used to sign in, not the business email of the account.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"1556c310-8f2c-480c-b826-53be2159d13a\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b4683d00-2dd9-4ee3-87b6-55851457b1c7\"><strong>PIN: </strong>A 6-digit PIN used to authorize Payouts and refund card charges.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"34d7cc87-21ed-4936-a623-b0f6399ad3dc\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"4981b187-70fa-49f3-b32a-6e6fc5174d38\"><a href=\"/v1/docs/set-up-2fa\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>2FA Authentication</strong></a><strong>: </strong>Additional security to authenticate your login.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8e43d8c3-8887-4ede-bf89-2aa4cebf6bc0\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"e009850e-fbcd-4ecb-b76b-2df98cc5639d\"><strong>Dashboard Timezone Preference: </strong>This setting will affect the time displayed on your dashboard and the time your <a href=\"/v1/docs/transactions-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">transaction report</a> will be sent (this will only your account, and not your team members’).</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"734590ee-e371-44f0-8274-451a59c77888\">Upgrading a non-incorporated business account to an incorporated business account</h2><p data-block-id=\"1837f697-b272-48f1-8435-03fe8f6422c8\">You can upgrade your account from an individual account to a business account by contacting help@xendit.co. Please ensure you've prepared the <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">required information and documents</a>.</p><p data-block-id=\"d1962286-8192-4415-ba2c-508527e7dd1f\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Your dashboard","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Dasbor Anda","Slug":"your-dashboard","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-rpyqq4-136\">Setelah Anda membuat akun, Anda akan diarahkan ke dasbor Anda. Sebelum mulai membuat transaksi, penting untuk dipahami bahwa dasbor Anda memiliki dua mode:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-k5m45y-137\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-l5h5ud-138\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-h43bu2-139\"><strong>Mode Tes</strong>: Bereksperimen dan biasakan diri Anda dengan fitur kami atau uji integrasi Anda secara menyeluruh menggunakan dana virtual. Dalam Mode Tes, transaksi Anda tidak bertransaksi dengan uang sungguhan, sehingga Anda dapat dengan aman menguji berbagai fitur dan fungsionalitas sebelum meluncurkan produksi live.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-ojlmfn-140\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-mv24dp-141\"><strong>Mode Live</strong>: Terima dan proses pembayaran nyata dari pelanggan Anda. Mode ini tersedia setelah akun Anda diaktifkan.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-m388x7-142\">Anda akan melihat label di sudut kiri bawah dasbor di bawah logo bisnis yang menunjukkan dengan jelas apakah Anda sedang dalam Mode Tes atau Mode Live.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"mcs2g7ma-u9dl5l-143\"><strong>Cara mengganti mode dasbor</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-wnd56v-144\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-95yh08-145\" src=\"https://docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_1800%2Cw_2880%2Fv1%2FDashboard%2FScreenshot_2024-06-28_at_16.06.31_cptfcg%3F_a%3DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"497\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"center\" datadisplay=\"inline\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"yes\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:497px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:497px;margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:497px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;color:transparent;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-unczi2-146\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-3t7ggn-147\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-4kth3h-148\">Klik <strong>nama bisnis</strong> Anda di sudut kiri bawah dasbor</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-25415o-149\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mb-uujzir-150\">Aktifkan atau nonaktifkan opsi <strong>Ubah ke Mode Tes / Live</strong>sesuai kebutuhan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-xhh5q3-151\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-kpm27o-152\">Saat Anda beralih ke Mode Tes, itu <strong>hanya akan berlaku untuk dasbor Anda sendiri dan bukan untuk anggota tim Anda</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-og22kg-153\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-ephmmx-154\">Dalam Mode Live, Anda juga dapat memilih untuk beralih kembali ke Mode Tes—ini tidak akan menghapus aktivitas Anda di Mode Live</p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-kzl7j1-155\">Detail bisnis dan profil Anda</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-86afq7-156\">Untuk melihat detail bisnis dan profil Anda, klik <strong>Edit Profil</strong>. Informasi yang Anda kirimkan saat membuat akun dan memverifikasi detail Anda akan ditampilkan di bagian <strong>Bisnis Anda</strong>. Jika Anda ingin memperbarui salah satu detail ini, silakan hubungi <a href=\"mailto:help@xendit.co\" translate=\"no\">help@xendit.co</a></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-1hhppx-157\">Di bawah <strong>Profil Anda</strong>, Anda akan dapat melihat detail berikut:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-9a9aa7-158\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-akf8h7-159\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-m6uxfj-160\"><strong>Email: </strong>Email yang Anda gunakan untuk masuk, bukan email bisnis akun.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-062ln7-161\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-fcigeu-162\"><strong>PIN: </strong>PIN 6 digit yang digunakan untuk mengotorisasi tagihan kartu <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/overview-4\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Payout</a> dan pengembalian dana.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7mc-pdznkp-163\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-sqxvxo-164\"><a href=\"/v1/docs/id/set-up-2fa\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>2FA</strong></a><a href=\"/docs/id/set-up-2fa\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\"><strong>Autentikasi 2FA</strong></a><strong>: </strong>Keamanan tambahan untuk mengautentikasi login Anda.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-1ga9yk-165\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-cnhcik-166\"><strong>Preferensi Zona Waktu Dasbor: </strong>Pengaturan ini akan memengaruhi waktu yang ditampilkan di dasbor Anda dan waktu <a href=\"/docs/id/transactions-report\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">laporan transaksi</a> Anda akan dikirim (ini hanya akan akun Anda, dan bukan anggota tim Anda).</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-2b7ja5-167\">Upgrade akun bisnis yang belum diinkorporasi ke akun bisnis yang sudah diinkorporasi</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-1ctqmc-168\">Anda dapat meng-upgrade akun Anda dari akun individu ke akun bisnis dengan menghubungi help@xendit.co. Pastikan Anda telah menyiapkan <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/create-account\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">detail dan dokumen yang diperlukan</a>.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcs2g7md-l5tnw4-169\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Dasbor Anda","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"แดชบอร์ดของคุณ","Slug":"your-dashboard","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p style=\"text-align:start;line-height:1.6rem;box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-blur:;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-saturate:;--tw-sepia:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;margin:1rem 0px;color:rgb(119, 119, 119);margin-block:0.8rem;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\" data-block-id=\"512ddfac-cd0d-4e7f-b859-0cf6c5f0d134\"><img data-block-id=\"8d23a595-2acf-4ec6-8c19-cc004ee578bb\" src=\"https://docs.xendit.co/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdpvzoteik%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fill%2Ch_1800%2Cw_2880%2Fv1%2FDashboard%2FScreenshot_2024-06-28_at_16.06.24_vbq7rl%3F_a%3DBATCr5fi0&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"636\" height=\"auto\